data.description: Welcome Home! Discover the charm of this beautifully maintained detached property nestled in the serene vicinity of Prospect Park. This residence is a perfect blend of modern amenities and natural beauty, designed to offer a warm and inviting living space. The convenience of off-street parking, with both a private driveway and ample street options, ensures that you're greeted with ease upon arrival. Step inside to find an interior bathed in natural light, accentuating the wooden floors that span throughout the home. Integrated ceiling fans in each room add to the comfort, circulating fresh air during those warm summer months. The heart of the home, the kitchen, boasts white quartz countertops providing both an elegant dining area and a spacious preparation surface. All kitchen appliances are fairly new. The layout seamlessly flows into a generous backyard featuring both greenery and a cemented patio, enclosed by a wooden fence, offering a tranquil outdoor retreat. Additional features include three spacious bedrooms, ample closet space, a full unfinished basement, full bath, recessed lighting, and so much more! Around the corner from regional railing and less than a mile from I95 for driving. This Prospect Park gem is more than a house; it's a canvas for your future memories, ready to welcome its new owner. Schedule your tour today!  DEADELINE for all offers will be Tuesday 4/23/24 . Seller will make a decision Wednesday 4/24/24 at 7pm.
